Angular 2,4

1.installation

npm install -g @angular/cli
2.creating
ng new APP_NAME
3.Running
ng serve
4.Building
ng build
5.base href
ng build --base-href=/my/app/
6.build for production
ng build --prod
7.Reduce the bundle size
ng build --prod --build-optimizer
8.Inspect the bundle we use source-map-explorer after production build we can inspect javascript code
npm install source-map-explorer --save-dev
9.tsconfig.json
TypeScript compiler configuration.
10.Ahead-of-Time (AOT), which compiles your app at build time.
ng build --aot
ng serve --aot


https://angular.io/guide/ajs-quick-reference
Unexpected token in angular2-jwt.ts when building with AOT compilation
https://github.com/auth0/angular2-jwt/issues/198

